  "detailed_description": "The Village - is a combination of SNES / PS1 J-RPG style games (like Secret of Evermore, Illusion of Time, Chrono Trigger, FFVI...) and riddle game. In addition to the labyrinths and enigma (high difficulty), you will find all the elements specific to the J-RPG (various characters and faculties, farming, crafting...) to allow you to progress and finish your quest.",
  "about_the_game": "The Village - is a combination of SNES / PS1 J-RPG style games (like Secret of Evermore, Illusion of Time, Chrono Trigger, FFVI...) and riddle game. In addition to the labyrinths and enigma (high difficulty), you will find all the elements specific to the J-RPG (various characters and faculties, farming, crafting...) to allow you to progress and finish your quest.",
